  66:./src/main.c  ****   * @brief Peripheral type mapping system
  67:./src/main.c  ****   * @details Creates a lookup system for peripheral base types, enabling generic
  68:./src/main.c  ****   *          register access macros to work across all TIM instances uniformly.
