  77:./src/main.c  ****   * @brief Type-safe register access macro
  78:./src/main.c  ****   * @note This performs a controlled cast that:
  79:./src/main.c  ****   *       - Ensures volatile access (critical for hardware registers)
  80:./src/main.c  ****   *       - Provides bitfield access through TIM1_CR1_t structure
  81:./src/main.c  ****   *       - Maintains strict type checking
